high_descs: Turn to your right, go to the stove.
Pick up the tea kettle on the back left burner.
Turn and walk to the table, stand at the table so that the soap dispenser is to the left and the salt shaker is to the right.
Place the tea kettle on the table to the left of the yellow apple and in front of the soap dispenser.
Turn around and go back to the stove.
Pick up the tea kettle located on the back right burner.
Turn and walk to the table, stand at the table so that the soap dispenser is to the left and the salt shaker is to the right.
Place the second tea kettle near the edge of the table behind the soap dispenser and to the left of the plant.
anns.task_desc: Move the two tea kettles from the stove to the table.

high_descs: Move to stove to the right of the refrigerator before the sink

Move to dining table in front of fridge
Place tea pot on the dining table
Move to stove to the right of the refrigerator before the sink
Pick up tea pot from back of stove
Move to dining table in front of fridge
Place tea pot on the dining table
anns.task_desc: Put the two tea pot on the stove to the kitchen table.

turn left and walk over to the kitchen table at the end of the room

turn left and walk to the table at the end of the room on the left
